```
-> (f 5)
-> (5 2)

;   given: 5

```

```
(define (sum-doubles a b)
  (if (> a b)
      0
      (+ (* 2 a) (sum-doubles (+ a 1) b))))    

(define (sum-squares a b)  
  (if (> a b)
      0
      (+ (square a) (sum-squares (+ a 1) b))))

(define (sum-cubes a b)
  (if (> a b)
      0
      (+ (cube a) (sum-cubes (+ a 1) b))))
```

```
(define (sum fn a b)
  (if (> a b)
      0
      (+ (fn a) (sum fn (+ a 1) b))))
```

```
(define (sum-squares a b)
  (sum square a b))

(define (sum-cubes a b)
  (sum cube a b))

(define (sum-doubles a b)
  (sum (lambda (x) (* 2 x)) a b)) 
```
